product.title: Pozyie Upgraded Diffuser for Dyson Airwrap Styler, Hair Dryer Diffuser Nozzle Attachment for Dyson for Airwrap HS05 HS03 HS01,Gold
product.description:
COMPATIBLE MODELS: Diffuser for Dyson Airwrap attachment, new upgraded diffuser nozzle, compatible with Dyson Airwrap Styler that converts into a hair dryer. Our diffuser is hassle-free to install and dependable to use.
HIGH QUALITY MATERIAL: The diffuser is made of high-quality material and has a large area to dry hair quickly, extended evenly spaced prongs disperses air evenly and deeply into hair, simulating natural drying and helping to reduce frizz and fly away.
UPGRADED DIFFUSER: The material and texture of this diffuser nozzle have been greatly upgraded compared to the original version. The airflow is smoother, the feel is more delicate, and the appearance is more refined. Flexible and lightweight design lets you easily control airflow and is suitable for all hair types.
THE BEST GIFT: This upgraded diffuser has good heat insulation function, ensuring safety and stability in use. This is a great gift for your classy wife, mother, friend and anyone!
PACKAGE CONTENTS: 1x Upgraded Diffuser for Dyson Airwrap. Diffuser nozzles can help you style your hair in any style, whether you have curly, wavy or straight hair. We provide after-sales support, you can contact us anytime!
